OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning mist and fog
OL,6,Fpatches should soon clear, perhaps
OL,7,Fgiving some morning brightness before
OL,8,Fbecoming increasingly cloudy through
OL,9,Fthe day with outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Farriving from the south from late
OL,11,Fmorning. Generally mild with light
OL,12,Fwinds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy overnight and turning
OL,15,Fincreasingly murky, with low cloud
OL,16,Fgiving the risk of mist and fog.
OL,17,FInitial outbreaks of rain will become
OL,18,Fmore patchy and drizzly as the night
OL,19,Fprogresses.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
