OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FMist and fog patches
OL,6,Fclearing during the morning, but
OL,7,Fremaining mostly cloudy with patchy
OL,8,Frain and drizzle. Perhaps a few
OL,9,Fbrighter spells during the afternoon,
OL,10,Fbefore becoming murky again overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMurky
OL,13,Fwith low cloud and patchy drizzle
OL,14,FSunday, though some afternoon breaks
OL,15,Fpossible. Dull at first Monday before
OL,16,Fbrightening with showers. Sunny spells
OL,17,FTuesday, turning cloudy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
